Direct Known Subclasses:
SoapOperationInboundConnectorBase
public abstract class GenericInboundConnectorBase extends InboundConnectorBase implements InboundConnectorDefinition<org.apache.camel.model.RoutesDefinition>
Base class for defining generic inbound connectors.

Adapter developers should extend this class and annotate it with @InboundConnector to specify the connector. The configuration of the inbound endpoint is done by overriding defineInitiatingEndpoint().

See Also:
